🛒 1. The E-Commerce Arena: Flipkart vs. Amazon vs. Myntra

Situation: You are a small Indian startup launching a new electronic gadget with a limited marketing budget.
Debate: Which platform offers the best opportunity for an exclusive product launch?

🟦 Team Flipkart: “The mass reach in Indian cities & trust of Indian consumers.”

🟧 Team Amazon: “Global visibility, logistics power, and Prime benefits.”

🟪 Team Myntra: “Niche appeal, influencer-driven marketing, and premium branding.”
